DocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tgk1665703136358.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tgk1665703136358.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tgk1665703136358.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tgk1665703136358\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__usetparm_408977\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the value of a ProcScript function.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__topic_d123998e1_d123999e1_d124000e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104tgk1665703136358_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__codeblock_rcb_wkk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long usetparm(shortcode, unsigned char*value, unsigned char*param);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__topic_d87577e1_d87578e1_d87579e1_d87580e1_d87581e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1103234e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__parml_c3z_wkk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">code</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Numeric code identifying the ProcScript function, as given in the table\n                  below.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Value, in string format, to be assigned to the ProcScript function.</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">param</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Parameter to the ProcScript function. Specify zero or an empty string if the\n                  function has no parameter.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__topic_d87582e1_d87583e1_d87584e1_d87585e1_d87586e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1103234e100\">Return Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__li_d45653e1_d45654e1_d45655e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—Success.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__li_d45656e1_d45657e1_d45658e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>—An error occurred, for\n               example, the specified field or entity does not exist.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__topic_d87587e1_d87588e1_d87589e1_d87590e1_d87591e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1103234e119\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__topic_d87592e1_d87593e1_d87594e1_d87595e1_d87596e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1103234e132\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__p_d124034e1_d124035e1_d124036e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">usetparm</code> sets the ProcScript\n            function identified by <var class=\"keyword varname\">code</var> to the value <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var>. If\n            the ProcScript function expects a numeric value, <var class=\"keyword varname\">value</var> should be the\n            string representation of that value. If the ProcScript function requires a parameter\n            (typically a field or entity name), that name should be passed in\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">param</var> in uppercase characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__p_d124037e1_d124038e1_d124039e1\">The following table lists the ProcScript functions, in alphabetical order, that can be used with <code class=\"ph codeph\">usetparm</code>. These functions are a subset of those that can be accessed with <code class=\"ph codeph\">usysparm</code>. For a numerically sorted list of ProcScript functions, see the 3GL function <code class=\"ph codeph\">usysparm</code> tables.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Functions accessible via usetparm</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\">Function</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">Param</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$batch</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">18</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">4004</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">4003</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldcheck</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3003</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3011</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldvalrep</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3010</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmod</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">1001</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formtitle</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">1006</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hide</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">4002</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancemod</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">7005</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$ioprint</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyboard</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">6</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occcheck</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">2010</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$prompt</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">1004</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3009</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$valrep</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">3008</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">Field</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>}}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__2\">5</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgk1665703136358__table_d14996e1_d14997e1_d14998e1__entry__3\">—</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__p_d124040e1_d124041e1_d124042e1\">For more information on ProcScript functions, see\n            the \"ProcScript: Functions\" topic.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following code uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">usetparm</code> to set the value of\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">$ioprint</code> to 255, and to set the <code class=\"ph codeph\">$fieldcheck</code>\n            function TRUE for the field CODE<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>LEDGER.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104tgk1665703136358_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"tgk1665703136358__codeblock_v2y_fmk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void setstuff ()\n{\n(void)usetparm(3,\"255\",0); /* Set $ioprint to 255 */\n(void)usetparm(3003,\"1\",\"CODE.LEDGER\"); /* Set $fieldcheck TRUE */\n/* for field CODE.LEDGER */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rfg1665702624715.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript: Functions</a><p>Refer to the topics under this section to understand functions related to ProcScript.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ftl1665703136439.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>usysparm</a><p>Call a ProcScript function and return its value.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532335\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532335\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "usetparm Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the value of a ProcScript function. Explain this code long usetparm(shortcode, unsigned char*value, unsigned char*param); Copy Parameters code Numeric code identifying the ProcScript function, as given in the table below. value Value, in string format, to be assigned to the ProcScript function. param Parameter to the ProcScript function. Specify zero or an empty string if the function has no parameter. Return Values 0 —Success. -1 —An error occurred, for example, the specified field or entity does not exist. Use Library: yrtl Description usetparm sets the ProcScript function identified by code to the value value . If the ProcScript function expects a numeric value, value should be the string representation of that value. If the ProcScript function requires a parameter (typically a field or entity name), that name should be passed in param in uppercase characters. The following table lists the ProcScript functions, in alphabetical order, that can be used with usetparm . These functions are a subset of those that can be accessed with usysparm . For a numerically sorted list of ProcScript functions, see the 3GL function usysparm tables. Table 1. Functions accessible via usetparm Function Code Param $batch 18 — $check 4004 — $disable 4003 — $fieldcheck 3003 { Field { . Entity }} $fieldproperties 3011 { Field { . Entity }} $fieldvalrep 3010 { Field { . Entity }} $formmod 1001 — $formtitle 1006 — $hide 4002 — $instancemod 7005 — $ioprint 3 — $keyboard 4 — $language 6 — $occcheck 2010 { Entity } $prompt 1004 — $properties 3009 { Field { . Entity }} $valrep 3008 { Field { . Entity }} $variation 5 — For more information on ProcScript functions, see the \"ProcScript: Functions\" topic. The following code uses usetparm to set the value of $ioprint to 255, and to set the $fieldcheck function TRUE for the field CODE . LEDGER. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void setstuff () { (void)usetparm(3,\"255\",0); /* Set $ioprint to 255 */ (void)usetparm(3003,\"1\",\"CODE.LEDGER\"); /* Set $fieldcheck TRUE */ /* for field CODE.LEDGER */ } Copy Related Links ProcScript: Functions Refer to the topics under this section to understand functions related to ProcScript. usysparm Call a ProcScript function and return its value. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}